         <div type="translation">
            <ab>recto: "(30. 21) ... with a strong hand, without pity you whipped me, (22) and you set me in pain. (23) I know that death will destroy me, for the home of all the dead is the earth. (24) Would that it were possible for me to kill myself or to beg another to do so for me. (25) I ...";verso: "(26) ... days .... evil days befell me. (27 omitted) (28) I was in never-silent sighing, I resided in an assembly, and I shouted. (29) I became friends with the ostriches and the sparrows, (30) and my skin and my bones became dark from the heat."</ab>
         </div>
